lead_paragraph: Kristaps Porzingis had 27 points and Carmelo Anthony added 25 to lead the New York Knicks to a 117-104 victory over the Bulls on Friday night in the triumphant return of Derrick Rose and Joakim Noah to Chicago.

headline.print_headline: Knicks Rally Past Bulls, 117-104, in Rose, Noah Homecoming
